<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/aug/22/">&#x27a0;</a> August 22, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="boston-red-sox-sunshine-state" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2007/08/22/sunshine_state/">Boston Red Sox - Sunshine state</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The Globe&#8217;s Gordon Edes, painting pictures with words:  &#8220;Ortiz was still light on his feet after the game, dancing in the buff back and forth in the shower room while singing over and over at the top of his lungs the theme from &#8220;Monday Night Football.&#8221; &#8220;Dah-dah-dah-DAH, dah-dah-dah-DAH,&#8221; sang Ortiz, apparently jacked up that the team&#8217;s fantasy football draft was about to commence as soon as he could find a towel.&#8221;</p>

<p>I&#8217;m not going to be able to shift that image from my brain for a while.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
